{
  "stem": "232.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we were in this movie house until one morning-- November 4, I think it was-- at 5 o'clock in the morning, Raus, auf raus, you know, the German voices-- broken in this movie house, broke the doors with, with [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] rifle butts, moved in, and turned over the beds.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Raus, raus.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And there were lorries outside already, trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they put us on trucks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "At this same moment, there was a little chaos, and my brother, luckily, went up the stairs where the balcony was-- where there was-- all the chairs were stored.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he went under the, the chairs, and he was never seen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They did not see him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So he was safe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We were taken on the-- on the-- to the trucks, with my friend, [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Ludie ?] Goldman, who was a good friend of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He went with us to Agde.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We met back in Italy together, in, in Saint-Martin-Vesubie.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we walked into Italy together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he and his father, and my father, who were friends from Germany, we were all together caught.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took us to Florence in a big [NON-ENGLISH, a big [NON-ENGLISH], military [NON-ENGLISH]-- and put us in the stables where the horses used to be.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And during the whole day, they brought in people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They prepared a transport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They brought people, and people, and people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went out to the bathroom during the day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I saw near the bathroom, there was a big-- there was about a 16-foot wall, but had hooks in it, in the wall.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to my friend this is a place where maybe tonight we can try to escape.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he saw it, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we decided to try it tonight.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
